---
title: Beyond Meat® and Sweet Pepper Tacos with Lime Crema and Salsa Fresca
description: A satisfying plate of tacos is just what the doctor ordered! For these handhelds, roasted peppers and onions are paired with seasoned Beyond Meat®, zesty lime crema and homemade salsa fresca.
